g.ns1:text: \n\\begin{align*}\n U^-_{i+\\frac12} & = \\overline{U}_i + \\frac{\\Delta x}{2}s_i\\\\\n U^+_{i+\\frac12} & = \\overline{U}_{i+1} - \\frac{\\Delta x}{2}s_{i+1}\\\\\n U^-_{i-\\frac12} & = \\overline{U}_{i-1} + \\frac{\\Delta x}{2}s_{i-1}\\\\\n U^+_{i-\\frac12} & = \\overline{U}_i - \\frac{\\Delta x}{2}s_i\\\\\n\\end{align*}
